-I stitched her up best I could.

82
00:05:31.333 --> 00:05:32.750
She'll live. unfortunately.

83
00:05:34.916 --> 00:05:36.833
That's for tasing me.

84
00:05:39.041 --> 00:05:40.708
That's for lying to me.

85
00:05:40.791 --> 00:05:42.125
