125
00:07:53.375 --> 00:07:55.208
Maybe I felt guilty.

126
00:07:55.291 --> 00:07:58.250
Maybe I was trying
to point him down the right path.

127
00:07:58.333 --> 00:08:00.791
You can't point down the right path

128
00:08:00.875 --> 00:08:03.708
