Hey. I didn't mean to rile you up
back in London.

230
00:16:57.708 --> 00:17:01.041
And Rome. And Tuscany. And France.

231
00:17:02.166 --> 00:17:03.791
That's all right. Don't worry about it.

232
00:17:03.875 --> 00:17:06.500
