250
00:18:02.041 --> 00:18:03.666
You're doing that.

251
00:18:05.250 --> 00:18:07.166
Keep doing it.

252
00:18:10.958 --> 00:18:12.000
[laughs]

253
00:18:12.083 --> 00:18:14.291
-[Sharpe] There we are.
-[Celine] Thank you.

254
00:18:16.250 --> 00:18:18.250
